OL,3,CArtist Helen Clapcott shows works at
OL,4,Cretrospective exhibition in her
OL,5,Chometown
OL,7,FVideo report by Paul Crone
OL,9,FAn artist who got everyone talking,
OL,10,Fwhen she displayed her work on three
OL,11,Fgiant billboards on a busy road in
OL,12,FStockport has been given her own
OL,13,Fexhibition in the town.
OL,15,FHelen Clapcott's paintings feature the
OL,16,Farchitectural history of Stockport
OL,17,Fover the decades. She has been
OL,18,Fcapturing the town on canvas since
OL,19,F1974, with some of her works taking
OL,20,Ftwo years to complete.
