OL,3,CArtist Helen Clapcott shows works at
OL,4,Cretrospective exhibition in her
OL,5,Chometown
OL,7,FWith a style reminiscent of Salford
OL,8,Fartist LS Lowry, Helen's work is
OL,9,Frenowned for her depictions of the
OL,10,Fpost-industrial landscape of her
OL,11,Fhometown. A result of meticulous
OL,12,Fsketches, her paintings reflect the
OL,13,Ftown's landmarks, like the former
OL,14,Fmills and the viaduct.
OL,16,FAnd from displaying her artwork on
OL,17,Fbillboards on a busy road in
OL,18,FStockport, back in 2022, Clapcott has
OL,19,Fnow moved to a more plush venue to
OL,20,Fdisplay her vivid images of the town.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
