OL,3,CArtist Helen Clapcott shows works at
OL,4,Cretrospective exhibition in her
OL,5,Chometown
OL,7,FShe has been given her own exhibition
OL,8,Fat the Stockport War Memorial Art
OL,9,FGallery, giving art lovers a chance to
OL,10,Fsee her work showing the town's
OL,11,Findustrial heritage through the
OL,12,Fdecades.
OL,14,FMore than one hundred of Helen's works
OL,15,Fwill be displayed, including flagship
OL,16,Fpieces The Power Station, The Last
OL,17,FCarnival and Brinksway 1979, Before
OL,18,FThe Motorway.
