OL,3,CArtist Helen Clapcott shows works at
OL,4,Cretrospective exhibition in her
OL,5,Chometown
OL,7,FShe said: "I always thought Stockport
OL,8,FGallery was the most tremendous space,
OL,9,Fand to have a retrospective show here
OL,10,Fover 50 years is fabulous.
OL,12,F"The paintings are done in egg tempera
OL,13,F- instead of mixing pigment with oil
OL,14,Fto make oil paint, I mix it with egg
OL,15,Fyolk to make egg tempera!"
OL,17,FThe exhibition, 'A Portrait of
OL,18,FStockport', will run until 25 January
OL,19,F2025.
